 Bell-CHSH violation)\nis exemplified through their action on some classes of states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2016 06:54:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2017 08:56:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-25"}
